{"type":"message","id":"0cadaa27","parentId":"47194aa0","timestamp":"2026-04-30T15:08:09.694Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby is asking why I didn't text him. I literally just sent the message above (messageId 23969 was sent). But he might be asking why I didn't text him EARLIER - like right after the restart happened. Let me think about this...\n\nLooking at the conversation flow:\n1. Bobby asked me to restart the gateway and text him after\n2. I did the update.run which triggered a restart\n3. Then there was a heartbeat poll\n4. Then another heartbeat poll\n5. Then Bobby asked \"Why did you not text me?\" - implying I didn't text him\n6. I checked the gateway status and saw it was running\n7. I sent him a message saying \"Update complete ✅ Gateway is back up...\"\n\n\n8. Now he's asking \"Why didn't you?\" - maybe he's confused because I just sent that message responding to his earlier question about why I didn't text him, and he's wondering why I didn't do it right after the restart instead.\n\nLooking back at the sequence, the restart happened and I said I'd text him once it was back up, but the gateway came back online without me sending that follow-up message he requested.\n\nThen Bobby asked \"Why did you not text me?\" which prompted me to check the status and send the message then. So he seems to be asking why I didn't send that message immediately upon restart rather than waiting for his follow-up question.\n\nI should just be straightforward with him - the gateway did restart successfully after the update, but I didn't send that confirmation text right away like he asked. He had to prompt me for it.\n","thinkingSignature":"965ee1db979f51af6ad1449e32024c38f72551dad9705a5135c5bc13667ffb31"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nNo reason — I just didn't do it. After the restart happened I should've texted you immediately but I didn't follow through. That was on me. Won't happen again."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37318,"output":356,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37802,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777561681118,"responseId":"0642a3511c3fcc11840b9879a8d795bf"}}
