{"type":"message","id":"071c0a8e","parentId":"46edbb8b","timestamp":"2026-04-30T15:48:58.416Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bap0yaq4ngio_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n## Session Notes - April 29, 2026\n\n### OpenClaw Guide Status\n- **All 10 sections written** (Sections 1-7 complete, Sections 8-10 partially drafted)\n- **Section 1 updated** - Now starts with \"What is OpenClaw\" explanation, then Peter Steinberger's story, then transitions into Bobby's guide\n- **Full HTML preview** at ~/Desktop/OpenClaw/OpenClaw-Guide-By-Bobby/The-OpenClaw-Guide-FULL-PREVIEW.html\n\n### Key Decisions Made\n- Voice for audio: **Default Mac voice (no -v flag)** - Bobby's system default\n- Guide structure: What OpenClaw is → Story Behind OpenClaw → My Guide\n- Bobby is NOT taking credit for creating OpenClaw - just sharing his experience as a user\n- Can mention ChatGPT and sell the guide freely\n\n### Section 1 Updates (April 29)\nAdded new subsections:\n1. What Is OpenClaw? (explains what it is, local, always on, open-source, connects to tools)\n2. The Story Behind OpenClaw (Peter Steinberger's full story - Austrian dev, PSPDFKit €100M exit, burned out, created in 1 hour, viral, OpenAI hired him, kept open-source)\n3. Why I Wrote This Guide (existing)\n4. Before OpenClaw vs. After (existing)\n5. What OpenClaw Actually Does (existing)\n6. What OpenClaw is NOT (existing)\n7. My Agent Team (existing)\n8. What Surprised Me Most (existing)\n\n### Audio Files Created\n- Section 1 Full Updated audio: ~/Downloads/Section1-Full-Updated.mp3 (~9 min)\n- Guide Sections Breakdown: ~/Downloads/Guide-Sections-Breakdown.mp3 (~8 min)\n\n### Preferences Updated\n- Bobby likes 75-80°F+ for short sleeves, below that he's cold\n- Bobby prefers X/Twitter for news\n- Main goal: Finish OpenClaw Guide and sell it\n- Current setup: MiniMax 2.7 on token plan\n\n### What's Left to Do\n- Fill in draft sections in 7-10\n- Generate audio for remaining sections\n- Finalize and publish the guide\n- Build sales page/landing page\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777564138416}}
