{"type":"message","id":"33160f69","parentId":"b56308ee","timestamp":"2026-05-01T00:42:34.741Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby needs a simple promissory note / loan repayment agreement between himself and his mom. This is a straightforward private loan document. Let me draft something simple and clear.\n","thinkingSignature":"56902062b4af6e7a175aaa65382ec9c760bc879fb037adc5adcd5214248cf911"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nGot it. Give me a minute.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z4othvd0t11w_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Promissory Note\n\n**Date:** April 30, 2026\n\n**Lender:** [Mom's Full Name]\n**Borrower:** Bobby Galletta\n\n---\n\n## Loan Terms\n\nOn the date above, the Lender loaned the Borrower **$13,000.00** (thirteen thousand dollars).\n\nIn consideration of this loan, the Borrower agrees to repay the Lender as follows:\n\n- **Total Payments:** 30 monthly payments of **$441.00** each\n- **Total Repayment:** $13,230.00\n- **First Payment Due:** May 31, 2026 (before midnight)\n- **Subsequent Payments Due:** The last day of each month thereafter until paid in full\n- **Final Payment Date:** On or before April 30, 2029\n\n## Payment Details\n\n- Payments shall be made via Zelle, cash, or other mutually agreed method\n- Each payment of **$441.00** shall be paid to the Lender by the due date\n- Borrower may pay off the remaining balance early without penalty\n\n## Default\n\nIf a payment is more than **10 days** late, the remaining balance may be declared immediately due and payable at Lender's discretion.\n\n## Governing Law\n\nThis agreement shall be governed by the laws of the State of Tennessee.\n\n---\n\n**Agreed and Accepted:**\n\n**Lender Signature:** _________________________ Date: _________\n\n**Print Name:** _________________________\n\n---\n\n**Borrower Signature:** _________________________ Date: _________\n\n**Print Name:** Bobby Galletta\n\n---\n\n*This is a private agreement between family members and is not a formal legal instrument. Both parties agree to the terms above in good faith.*","path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/Mom-Loan-Agreement.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43110,"output":426,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43664,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777596144603,"responseId":"064329f1c4a1f5eeec91355028a547dd"}}
