{"type":"message","id":"be0391bf","parentId":"4e48e64f","timestamp":"2026-05-01T00:43:26.190Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants the file sent to him on Telegram so he can open it on his iPhone. I'll send it as a document. Also I need to remove the interest - just $13,000 flat with $441 payments until paid off. Let me calculate: $13,000 / $441 = 29.47 months, so 30 payments of $441 = $13,230 but he says flat $13,000. Let me adjust.\n\nActually he said no interest - just 13,000 flat. So $13,000 total repaid. At $441/month that comes to about 29.5 months. So maybe 30 payments of $441 = $13,230 but he's saying flat $13,000. \n\n\nI think the simplest approach is to just divide $13,000 by the monthly payment amount to get the number of payments needed - that works out to about 30 payments of $441 with the last one being around $370. Or I could structure it as $441 monthly until the $13,000 is paid off. Let me update the document to reflect the straight $13,000 repayment with no interest.\n","thinkingSignature":"38fd1dd4329edf1ab95c8129e587909c35b6eaa1e11362958c05a15d227e243b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_zrym90llyghl_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"## Loan Terms\n\nOn the date above, the Lender loaned the Borrower **$13,000.00** (thirteen thousand dollars).\n\nIn consideration of this loan, the Borrower agrees to repay the Lender as follows:\n\n- **Monthly Payment:** **$441.00** per month\n- **Total Repayment:** $13,000.00 (no interest)\n- **Number of Payments:** 30 payments ($441 × 29 months + $391 final payment)\n- **First Payment Due:** May 31, 2026 (before midnight)\n- **Subsequent Payments Due:** The last day of each month thereafter until paid in full\n- **Estimated Payoff Date:** On or before October 31, 2029","oldText":"## Loan Terms\n\nOn the date above, the Lender loaned the Borrower **$13,000.00** (thirteen thousand dollars).\n\nIn consideration of this loan, the Borrower agrees to repay the Lender as follows:\n\n- **Total Payments:** 30 monthly payments of **$441.00** each\n- **Total Repayment:** $13,230.00\n- **First Payment Due:** May 31, 2026 (before midnight)\n- **Subsequent Payments Due:** The last day of each month thereafter until paid in full\n- **Final Payment Date:** On or before April 30, 2029"}],"path":"/Users/bobbygalletta/Desktop/Mom-Loan-Agreement.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43652,"output":584,"cacheRead":128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44364,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777596195420,"responseId":"06432a23daadc141fce5aaeff24894ff"}}
